data.description: Come see this comfortable home nestled in a well-maintained neighborhood that's close to many great amenities! Sporting a bi-level floor plan, one can head upstairs to find the kitchen that has an eating bar along with an adjacent dining room that sports a window seating area, a cozy and well-lit family room, and the main bedroom. The kitchen has a newer refrigerator as well as a newer stove/range. Head downstairs, you will find a warm family room with ample natural lighting that also features a fireplace where you can snuggle up on the sofa and enjoy the beauty of winter, which is coming soon!  There's also two bedrooms and a full bath on that level as well as a utility room that houses the washer/dryer, HVAC system and a new hot water heater.  The backyard is large and enclosed with a privacy fence, good for containing your children and pets.  Wineteer Elementary School is just a block away from this property.
